Package com.bobocode.bring.core.context.type

Class AbstractValueTypeInjector

java.lang.Object
com.bobocode.bring.core.context.type.AbstractValueTypeInjector
Direct Known Subclasses:
FieldInterfaceValueTypeInjector, FieldListValueTypeInjector, FieldMapValueTypeInjector, FieldQueueValueTypeInjector, FieldSetValueTypeInjector, ParameterInterfaceValueTypeInjector, ParameterListValueTypeInjector, ParameterMapValueTypeInjector, ParameterQueueValueTypeInjector, ParameterSetValueTypeInjector
public abstract class AbstractValueTypeInjector extends Object
The AbstractValueTypeInjector is an abstract class that serves as a base for value type injectors. It provides methods for injecting dependencies for types like List and Set. This injector collaborates with the AnnotationBringBeanRegistry and ClassPathScannerFactory equivalents to resolve bean names, retrieve or create beans, and inject dependencies based on the provided value types.
Since:
1.0
Author:
Blyzhnytsia Team
